 \frac{k!}{(1-x)^{k+1}} = \frac{d^k}{dx^k}\sum_{n=0}^\infty x^n     = \sum_{n=0}^\infty \frac{d^k}{dx^k}x^n     = \sum_{n=k}^\infty n\cdot (n-1)\cdots (n-k+1) x^{n-k}, 
